&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IDLE (Python's Built-in Editor)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="code console literal-block"&gt;
&lt;span class="go"&gt;idle file.py&lt;/span&gt;
